songs.title: Whip (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Uh-uh, yeah
Whippin' again, whippin'
Yeah

[Bridge]
They don't wanna see Push again
They don't wanna see 'Ye, he gone
They don't want nothin' like 2 Chainz
They don't wanna throw trees on
They don't want it like that
Whippin' again, whippin' again, whippin' again
Uh, they don't really wanna want the Pusha, baby
They don't really wanna-wanna call 'Ye
They don't really wanna kidnap for life
They don't wanna whip it in the same place
That just sippin' on the–, yeah

[Chorus]
Whippin' again, whippin' again, whippin' again, yeah
Back at again, back at again, back at again
All winter, all summer, Range Rovers and black Hummers
Bottles and [?], uh-uhs and go dummer
Whippin' again, whippin' again, whippin' again, yeah
In again, uh, back at again
All winter, all summer, uh, yeah
Yeah, yeah
Back in the bill, whippin' again, once again, yeah
Out in the East, park up the Benz on the sand, yeah
Skrrt off the–
(Punch me right there)
